'''Redhaven''' was the capital city of [[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamool]]. [[Tamaktis Breetha]] was once its [[Mayor/Legends|mayor]]. It was the site of the [[Square of Hopeful Redemption]], a pit located at the local [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport's]] former [[Portmaster's Pavilion]] where the [[Red Knights of Life]], led by [[Nom Anor]], stoned [[Droid/Legends|droids]] before destroying them.

